sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Web as Web / Mobile App
    participant Search as Search Service
    participant Cache as Redis / OpenSearch
    participant Booking as Booking Manager
    participant DB as Transactional Database
    participant Pay as Payment Service
    participant Provider as External Provider
    participant Events as Event Bus

    User->>Web: Search route and date
    Web->>Search: Search request
    Search->>Cache: Read indexed listings and cached prices
    Cache-->>Search: Candidate inventory
    Search-->>Web: Ranked results
    User->>Web: Select option
    Web->>Booking: Create idempotent hold
    Booking->>DB: Atomic inventory check and decrement
    DB-->>Booking: Hold created with expiry
    Booking-->>Web: Booking review and quoted price
    User->>Web: Confirm simulated payment
    Web->>Pay: Authorize using idempotency key
    Pay-->>Booking: Approved or declined
    alt Payment approved
        Booking->>Provider: Revalidate and reserve
        alt Provider confirms
            Provider-->>Booking: Confirmation reference
            Booking->>DB: Mark CONFIRMED
            Booking->>Events: Publish BookingConfirmed
            Booking-->>Web: Confirmation
        else Provider timeout or rejection
            Booking->>DB: Release inventory
            Booking->>Pay: Compensating refund
            Booking->>Events: Publish BookingFailed
            Booking-->>Web: Safe failure state
        end
    else Payment declined
        Booking->>DB: Release inventory
        Booking-->>Web: Payment failure state
    end
